text: Cameo Kirby can refer to: * Cameo Kirby (play), a 1909 Broadway play written by Booth Tarkington and Harry Leon Wilson, or its three screen adaptations: ** Cameo Kirby (1914 movie), a 1914 silent American movie ** Cameo Kirby (1923 movie), a 1923 silent American movie ** Cameo Kirby (1930 movie), a talkie by Fox Film Corporation
